2e8def83fbb60fa3c1b0c1","tid":1387157,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:50:58.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNk%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=542ecce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。"},{"pid":"4a00a1904b377dcd29684c49a3d27551cb659f0d","tid":1387157,"uid":53530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:54:15.000Z","msg":"我植完 生出黎d頭髮好似尻毛咁捲 有咩方法處理 定係正常?"},{"pid":"212d150ac807d52b0f084671c78f69bb4ac38b55","tid":1387157,"uid":237115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73a3ea6c69fba33cd6705ba8269d8689a61b17c6","tid":1387157,"uid":181551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:39:57.000Z","msg":"想問下點解會有條疤痕？ 係唔係做植髮會有疤痕 ？謝謝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:25:40.000Z","msg":"師兄，植髮手術係由後腦區取髮，再植落去禿嘅位置。<br />\n<br />\n我做嗰隻手術叫 FUT，係喺後腦區鎅一條頭皮出嚟，呢種方法傳統啲，但平啲 (當時我 budget 好緊張&hellip;&hellip;)<br />\n<br />\n有一隻新啲嘅手術，叫 FUE，都係喺後腦區取髮，不過係用機器逐個毛囊咁樣取頭髮，做完會有「非常不明顯嘅疤痕」，咁費用當然係貴些少。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩種植髮手術嘅圖片、過程、復原時間等資料，請瀏覽下面個page，謝。<br />\n<a href=\"https://gethairpro.tw/fue-vs-fut/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgethairpro.tw%2Ffue-vs-fut%2F&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNk%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=cdd0fad2\" target=\"_blank\">https://gethairpro.tw/fue-vs-fut/</a>"},{"pid":"67dabdfc40ef7b1b4d681eafbd4886ce40388048","tid":1387157,"uid":237115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a00a1904b377dcd29684c49a3d27551cb659f0d","tid":1387157,"uid":53530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:54:15.000Z","msg":"我植完 生出黎d頭髮好似尻毛咁捲 有咩方法處理 定係正常?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"咁奇怪？你喺邊度植呀？師兄本身係直頭髮？有冇天然攣？<br />\n<br />\n植髮係取自身體本身嘅頭髮，植落想植嘅位置，毛囊同髮質喺植完之後，會維持一樣。<br />\n<br />\n身體唔同部位嘅毛髮，捲曲度唔同，為咗效果美觀，一般都係用返後腦區頭髮嚟植，除非數量超唔夠，如果唔係都好少用其他部位嚟湊夠數。"},{"pid":"ed223e79ee67083d129d39b8e08a3e8f44338ee5","tid":1387157,"uid":237115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16616245603f6296e82e8def83fbb60fa3c1b0c1","tid":1387157,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:50:58.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNk%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=542ecce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"師兄，我禿頭，係因為遺傳咗阿爸嘅脫髮基因 (i.e. 雄性禿)，唔係丁得多，不過都絕對同意丁太多對身體唔好，多謝提醒。<br />\n<br />\n【歡迎參考】<br />\n自我檢測有冇雄性禿，搵出治療方法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gethairpro.tw/androgenetic-alopecia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgethairpro.tw%2Fandrogenetic-alopecia%2F&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNk%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=8d7f5e6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://gethairpro.tw/androgenetic-alopecia/</a>"},{"pid":"4fe1f9f84197455aed0965d0bca30d062d51db7e","tid":1387157,"uid":53530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67dabdfc40ef7b1b4d681eafbd4886ce40388048","tid":1387157,"uid":237115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a00a1904b377dcd29684c49a3d27551cb659f0d","tid":1387157,"uid":53530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:54:15.000Z","msg":"我植完 生出黎d頭髮好似尻毛咁捲 有咩方法處理 定係正常?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"咁奇怪？你喺邊度植呀？師兄本身係直頭髮？有冇天然攣？<br />\n<br />\n植髮係取自身體本身嘅頭髮，植落想植嘅位置，毛囊同髮質喺植完之後，會維持一樣。<br />\n<br />\n身體唔同部位嘅毛髮，捲曲度唔同，為咗效果美觀，一般都係用返後腦區頭髮嚟植，除非數量超唔夠，如果唔係都好少用其他部位嚟湊夠數。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"我係直  都係用後腦  仁安植